headline.main: In Rare Reversal, Ohio Court Overturns Cocaine Filler Case
headline.print_headline: In Rare Reversal, Ohio Court Overturns Cocaine Filler Case

lead_paragraph: Ohio's top court ruled Monday that sentences for suspects caught with cocaine can be based on the weight of the entire amount, which could include filler material such as baking soda.
